  <front>
   <head>Upon Julia's Clothes</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="tercet">
     <l n="1" met="-+-+-+-+">Whenas in silks my Julia goes,</l>
     <l n="2" met="++-+-+-+">Then, then (methinks) how sweetly flows</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+-+-+-+">That liquefaction of her clothes.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="tercet">
     <l n="4" met="+--+-+-+">Next, when I cast mine eyes and see </l>
     <l n="5" met="-+-+-+++">That brave vibration each way free,</l>
     <l n="6" met="+--+--+-+">O how that glittering taketh me!</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
